message.entry: Config type ''{0}'' not supported for GPU code generation.
Expected a nonempty string array, a character vector, or a cell array of character vectors.
Expected dlnetwork input to be initialized.
Code generation for quantized network is not supported.
GPU Code generation supports only the CUDA and OpenCL target languages.
Deep Learning code generation for CPUs or GPUs requires MATLAB Coder Interface for Deep Learning support package or GPU Coder Interface for Deep Learning support package.
Classes property of layer ''{0}'' contains non-ASCII characters. For code generation, the Classes property must contain ASCII characters only.
